.TH devin-skills 1  "skills " 
.SH NAME
devin\-skills \- Manage agent skills (slash commands and agent\-triggered context blobs)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin skills\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage agent skills (slash commands and agent\-triggered context blobs)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
devin\-skills\-list(1)
List all available skills
.TP
devin\-skills\-show(1)
Show details for a specific skill
.TP
devin\-skills\-paths(1)
Show skill directory locations
.TP
devin\-skills\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
